        "TileImage": "$($repository c6fe1c64-2ad7-4548-9581-8b80026a8c1f).Image",
        "Description": "Good Evening, 47.\r\rI&apos;ll be honest, I&apos;ve come across a rather annoying complication.\rI will be attending the Moonlight Gala in Canada, to celebrate the 100th Anniversarry of the Group of Seven, and I would like to go in style.\rThe Red Dress I want has been taken.\r\rYour target, is Edwina Endicott. \r\rYou know the type, Supermodel turned Spy Master. She is currently attending the Dartmoor Garden show, and is a very social person.\rI want the dress in good condition, 47. Do your thing.",
